rComments: I have taken 3 courses with Prof. Cote. Hes fantastic. I love how much material we can get through in class, and then I leave feeling more energetic than when I came in (cannot stand sleep-inducing lectures). His lectures are fantastic, he is so engaging. Hes also kind, extremely knowledgeable and very good humoured. 100% recommend.

Very theatrical guy - he'll use different voices for different philosophers in mock conversations, and it's the best. Listening and watching him talk is so entertaining. He knows his stuff although not always clear transitions between thoughts. I am taking another course with him and looking forward to it. Not much technology use - write good notes
Well-organized lectures, clearly prepared and knowledgeable. Conveys material well with good intonation, involves students. Easy to talk to. Interesting material. Very fair final.
